data.description: MLS# 14673702 - Built by Pacesetter Homes - Ready Now! ~ This beautiful new Pacesetter Home in fast-growing Royse City offers a 3 bedroom, study with an open-concept living, fireplace, Garden Tub and Shower in the Master bath and 3 car tandem garage, perfect for that extra storage or workshop. The Coppell plan is one of our most popular floor plans, and if you come out to look its easy to see why! Located in the Woodland Creek community including a community pool, half basketball court and walking trail.  See you soon!!
